  "description": {
    "zh": "过来，过来。最近不断有空投物资送来，我们的任务是尽可能把它们截胡。如果那群混蛋把迫击炮玩明白了，事态就难以控制了。\n\n尽你所能，把能找到的东西都带给我。我会给你丰厚的报酬。",
    "en": "Come on in. The airdrops keep coming in, and our job is to hold on to whatever we can intercept. If these assholes have mastered mortars, they'll be unstoppable with EWs and spare parts for them.\n\nBring me everything you can get. I'll prepare a good reward."
